metadata.name: My House
metadata.description:
No matter what 'home' means to you, there is definitely something nostalgic about the places we call home. It is a place where we eat, a place with friends and family, where we enjoy the things and decorations of our homes, and it is a place to view our own old memories.  
Home is a physical manifestation of the people who live in it, so it's no wonder that home is a special place for many people. For most, home has taken on a very significant meaning over the past year. With more time spent at home than ever before, there are more stories left to remember for the future.

Date Created : 29/03/23
